transcripts:
-Hello, I am here  with Jeff. We are at the Bikes, Blues, and BBQ in Fayetteville, Arkansas. He came up to me and told me that he has one of our Char-Broiled TRU-Infrared. He's actually got our gourmet series and a 3 burner. So you came up to me and you told me what? 

-I told you that we love the grill. It's the best one we've ever had. And it just makes all the food juicy and it locks in the flavor. Everything tastes better than it ever did before. It's-- no flare ups. We use a lot less propane than we did before. It just turned out to be the best grill we've had. 

-Well, thank you, Jeff, for coming up and telling us all about your Char-Broil TRU-Infrared.
